snippet.title: DARK SOULS II Hollow Lullaby Trailer (PS3)
snippet.description:
Don't miss the hardest game you'll ever love. Explore a vast breathtaking world filled with mythical monsters & murderous bosses. It's about the journey, not the destination.

Pre-orders at participating retailers will be upgraded to the Black Armor Edition for FREE while supplies last!

http://www.darksoulsii.com
